Stress

Stress is related to Shock, Sway (at up to Twist Levels), RT, Wounds, and Hitches.

Stress is created by Stressors

Stressors include:
	 Size Annexes on Force of Nature / Kaiju Characters
	 Combat Stress: Seeing (whether taking or making) Wounds should have a Stress component.
	 Major Life Events: These all create Stress, but are sometimes positive in nature
